LATEST PEOPLE'S CHOICE AWARDS NEWS PLUS WINNERS, AND NOMINEES

Sex/Life co-stars and real life couple Sarah Shahi, 41, and Adam Demos, 36, make their red carpet debut at the People's Choice Awards Sarah Shahi and Adams Demos made their red carpet debut at The People's Choice Awards. They star in Sex/Life, which was nominated for The Bingeworthy Show of 2021. Sex/Life co-stars Sarah Shahi and Adam Demos make red carpet debut

Chelsea Handler sizzles in a plunging black and white gown as she makes red carpet debut with boyfriend Jo Koy at 2021 People's Choice Awards The 46-year-old comedian rocked a plunging black-and-white gown for the star-studded show where she picked up the Comedy Act trophy for her Vaccinated and Horny tour. Chelsea Handler makes red carpet debut with Jo Koy at People's Choice

Addison Rae wows in floral patterned dress and statement choker for People's Choice Awards in LA She's a social media star, actress and singer. And on Tuesday, Addison Rae dressed to the nines for the People's Choice Awards, which took place in Santa Monica at Barker Hangar. Addison Rae wows in floral patterned dress and statement choker

'Everyone is watching this show, it's crazy!' Natalie Zea shows off her chest in PLUNGING gown at People's Choice Awards as she talks La Brea success When at the People's Choice Awards on Tuesday, the blonde bombshell said that she is blown over by how popular the show is: 'Everyone is watching it!' she told Laverne Cox. La Brea star Natalie Zea shows off her chest in PLUNGING gown

Kim Kardashian makes a dash for her car as this year's Fashion Icon leads the 2021 People's Choice Awards departures with glamorous Halle Berry, Cardi B and Dorit Kemsley The TV personality was soon followed by actress Halle Berry, rapper Cardi B and Real Housewives of Beverly Hills star Dorit Kemsley after a memorable night at Barker Hangar. Kim Kardashian makes a dash for her

People's Choice Awards: Christina Aguilera, 40, gives a nod to her iconic Dirrty ensemble in chaps and sexy yellow bodysuit to scoop Icon gong... 19 years after first rocking the look The Genie in a Bottle songstress, 40, put on a sexy display in black and yellow chaps and a bodysuit for the star-studded event at the Barker Hangar in Santa Monica. Christina Aguilera gives a nod to her iconic Dirrty look

Selling Sunset's Christine Quinn and Emma Hernan stun in racy black ensembles as they lead castmates from their Netflix reality series at People's Choice Awards Selling Sunset stars Christine Quinn and Emma Hernan donned matching black dresses as they made their way down the red carpet at the People's Choice Awards in Santa Monica. Christine Quinn, Emma Hernan dress in black for People's Choice Awards

Ellen DeGeneres, Portia de Rossi, Kris Jenner, and Corey Gamble MATCH in red and black outfits at People's Choice Awards... as chat show host wins daytime talk show honor Ellen DeGeneres and her wife Portia de Rossi matched outfits with pals Kris Jenner and boyfriend Corey Gamble as they hung out at the People's Choice Awards on Tuesday night. Ellen DeGeneres, Portia de Rossi, Kris Jenner, and Corey Gamble MATCH

Cardi B showcases her famous curves in a VERY busty pink sparkly dress at the People's Choice Awards The rapper, 29, put on a very busty display in the floor-length plunging gown as she shot out a sultry look to cameras while working her angles. Cardi B showcases her famous curves at the People's Choice Awards

Becky G puts sets pulses racing with VERY leggy display in yellow dress featuring extremely high split at 2021 People's Choice Awards The 24-year-old singer - born Rebbeca Marie Gomez - put on a scintillating display in a very revealing gown at the 2021 People's Choice Awards on Tuesday. Becky G in yellow dress with VERY high split at People's Choice Awards

Christina Aguilera electrifies crowd with medley of hits including Beautiful and Fighter as she is presented with Music Icon gong at People's Choice Awards where H.E.R. and Blake Shelton perform Christina Aguilera electrified the crowd with a medley of her hits as she hit the stage Tuesday night for the People's Choice Awards in Los Angeles where she got the Music Icon gong. Christina wows at People's Choice Awards where H.E.R. and Blake sing

Euphoria star Sydney Sweeney takes the plunge in VERY low-cut black and white mini dress at People's Choice Awards Sydney Sweeney took to the red carpet at the People's Choice Awards and showed off some skin as she posed for photos. The actress, 24, donned an black skirt and a white bow covering her torso Sydney Sweeney attends People's Choice Awards in revealing dress

Kim Kardashian says designers were 'probably talked into' dressing her by Kanye West... as she accepts Fashion Icon trophy at People's Choice Awards In a touching speech, Kim couldn't help but give a shout out to Kanye, 44, who she filed for divorce from in February Kim Kardashian pays tribute to Kanye at People's Choice Awards

Tarek El Moussa kisses wife Heather Rae Young as they bring newlywed bliss to People's Choice Awards Tarek El Moussa kissed his new wife Heather Rae Young at the People's Choice Awards this Tuesday. The couple exuded newlywed bliss as they walked the red carpet hand in hand. Tarek El Moussa kisses Heather Rae Young at People's Choice Awards

Dorit Kemsley dares to bare in a VERY revealing dress as she leads the RHOBH cast arrivals at the People's Choice Awards The 45-year-old fashion designer and Housewife looked stunning in a very revealing cut-out gown, that showcased her stunning figure. Dorit Kemsley in very revealing dress at People's Choice Awards

Jojo Siwa dons gorgeous pink dress as she walks the red carpet at the 2021 People's Choice Awards Jojo Siwa wore a very classy ensemble as she walked the red carpet at the 2021 People's Choice Awards. The Dance Moms star, 18, wore a pink gown with a deep V that ended in the middle of her chest. Jojo Siwa dons gown as she walks red carpet at People's Choice Awards

Sarah Hyland kisses fiance Wells Adams who helps her with her dress as they walk red carpet for People's Choice Awards Sarah Hyland kissed her fiance Wells Adams on the People's Choice Awards red carpet in Los Angeles this Tuesday. The 31-year-old Modern Family actress also got a bit of assistance with her dress from him. Sarah kisses Wells who helps her with her dress at People's Choice

Chrishell Stause debuts new BRUNETTE hairdo as she rocks the lady in red look on the People's Choice Awards red carpet Chrishell Stause debuted her new brunette hairdo at the People's Choice Awards in Los Angeles this Tuesday. The 40-year-old is known for starring on the Netflix reality series Selling Sunset. Chrishell debuts BRUNETTE hairdo on People's Choice Awards red carpet

Paris Jackson exudes saucy throwback vibe in frilly brown frock and fishnets on People's Choice Awards red carpet Paris Jackson brought a saucy throwback vibe to the People's Choice Awards at the Barker Hangar in Santa Monica this Tuesday. The 23-year-old is the daughter of the late Michael Jackson. Paris Jackson exudes saucy throwback vibe at People's Choice Awards

2021 People's Choice Awards red carpet: Kim Kardashian turns heads in a lace Balenciaga look as she leads the glamour alongside Halle Berry, Cardi B and Scarlett Johansson The E! icon, 41, turned every head in a lace ensemble which hugged every curve of her famous body as she posed backstage with her gold Fashion Icon award. 2021 People's Choice Awards red carpet: Kim Kardashian wows

Christina Aguilera to receive People's Choice Awards 2021 Music Icon Award at upcoming ceremony Christina Aguilera's latest accolade is a Music Icon Award to be presented at this year's People's Choice Awards on December 7. It will be presented by the singer's recent collaborator Becky G. Christina Aguilera to receive People's Choice Awards' Music Icon Award

Kim Kardashian to be honored with the Fashion Icon Award at upcoming 2021 People's Choice Awards The star 'will be honored for her keen fashion sense, her unprecedented entrepreneurial success, and single-handedly transforming the fashion industry through her innovative designs.' Kim Kardashian set to receive Fashion Icon Award

Dwayne 'The Rock' Johnson will be presented with the People's Champion Award at the 2021 People's Choice Awards The Red Notice actor will receive the accolade December 7 in recognition for his contribution to the entertainment industry and entrepreneurial endeavor. Dwayne 'The Rock' Johnson will be honored at People's Choice Awards

Halle Berry set to be honored with The People's Icon award at the forthcoming 2021 People's Choice Awards The news about the 55-year-old actress-director was initially announced on Friday, when it was made known to the public that she would be honored for her contributions to the entertainment industry. Halle Berry set to be honored at the People's Choice Awards

Saturday Night Live vet Kenan Thompson will host the 2021 People's Choice Awards: 'I'm beyond blessed... good times!' This year, Thompson received his first-ever People's Choice Awards nominations and is up for both the 2021 Comedy TV Star and Male TV Star for his work on Saturday Night Live. Kenan Thompson will host the 2021 People's Choice Awards

People's Choice Awards 2021 nominations: F9: The Fast Saga revs up with eight nods while Loki earns four and Cobra Kai scores three The nominees for the 2021 People's Choice Awards have been announced. F9: The Fast Saga has the most nominations with eight, while Loki leads TV with four nominations and Cobra Kai with three. People's Choice Awards 2021 nominations: F9: The Fast Saga revs up

Black-ish star Tracee Ellis Ross jokes that being named a Fashion Icon 'was validation for my shopping habit' The actress, 48, was honored with the E! People's Choice Awards Fashion Icon Award in November. Tracee Ellis Ross jokes about being named a Fashion Icon on Ellen

Ellen DeGeneres flashes a peace sign while out to lunch with a friend... after winning People's Choice Award for her daytime talk show amid toxic workplace allegations Ellen DeGeneres looked to be in high spirits when she flashed a peace sign while out to lunch with a friend in Montecito, California on Friday. Ellen DeGeneres flashes peace sign during lunch outing with a friend

Ellen DeGeneres thanks 'amazing' staff while accepting best talk show at People's Choice Awards amid toxic workplace allegations: 'They give a 100 percent of themselves' The 62-year-old television personality took home the Daytime Talk Show award on Sunday night as she quickly shifted focus to those working on her Ellen DeGeneres Show months after controversy. Ellen DeGeneres thanks 'amazing' crew amid toxic workplace allegations

'I'm so excited to bring this baby boy into the world!' Pregnant Mandy Moore calls husband Taylor Goldsmith the 'love of her life' as she prepares to become a mother for the first time The This Is Us actress, 36, made the heartwarming remarks as she accepted the award for the Drama TV Star of 2020 for her role as Rebecca Pearson in the NBC drama series, on Sunday Pregnant Mandy Moore says she's 'so excited' to become a mother

Selling Sunset's Chrishell Stause debuts her new bangs as she attends People's Choice Awards with co-star Mary Fitzgerald amid DWTS partner Gleb Savchenko's marital drama The Selling Sunset personality, 39, brushed aside the drama as she debuted her new fringe alongside Mary, also 39, at this year's E! People's Choice Awards at the Barker Hangar on Sunday. Chrishell Stause debuts bangs at People's Choice with Mary Fitzgerald

Jameela Jamil makes a bold style statement in an oversized pink trouser suit adorned with a flower corsage at People's Choice Awards The Good Place star, 34, opted for a pink oversized trouser suit which included a double breasted blazer with shoulder pads. People's Choice Awards: Jameela Jamil wears bold pink trouser suit

Mindy Kaling makes her first appearance at the PCAs since giving birth where she won Best Comedy TV Show for Never Have I Ever Mindy Kaling made her first public appearance since giving birth to her second child in early September at the 2020 People's Choice Awards. Mindy Kaling makes her first appearance at the PCAs since giving birth

Chris Pratt's animated movie Onward wins the People's Choice Award for Best Family Movie after controversial plea for votes A controversial Instagram post from Chris Pratt asking fans to vote for his Disney Pixar movie Onward has paid off at the 2020 People's Choice Awards. Chris Pratt's animated movie Onward wins the People's Choice Award

Blake Shelton thanks his new fiancee Gwen Stefani during his win at 2020 People's Choice Awards The 44-year-old country singer joked about Stefani's massive fame as he showed his gratitude for her in the speech. Blake Shelton thanks fiancee Gwen Stefani in win at People's Choice

Sofia Vergara looks ravishing in red as she accepts her final People's Choice Award for Modern Family: 'The show that changed my life' The Colombian talent, 48, looked ravishing in red Dolce And Gabbana as she took to stage and spoke about how meaningful the award was to her. Sofia Vergara stuns in scarlet as she accepts People's Choice Award

Jennifer Lopez issues plea for healing and unity in tearful speech as she's honored at 2020 People's Choice Awards The singer and actress, 51, was presented with the People's Icon Of 2020 award at the ceremony in Santa Monica, California. Jennifer Lopez gives tearful speech at 2020 People's Choice Awards

Justin Bieber performs Lonely and Holy at the 2020 People's Choice Awards Justin Bieber performed two of his most recent songs, Lonely and Holy, at the 2020 People's Choice Awards on Sunday night. Justin Bieber performs Lonely and Holy at the 2020 PCAs

Christina Hendricks teases substantial cleavage in metallic Marchesa gown at People's Choice Awards The 45-year-old Mad Men alum announced that the winner of The Drama TV Star of 2020 trophy was This Is Us actress Mandy Moore Christina Hendricks dons Marchesa gown at People's Choice Awards

Black-ish star Tracee Ellis Ross is a boss in tailored suit with statement gold earrings at 2020 People's Choice Awards Ross' chosen outfit comprised a double-breasted jacket with gold buttons and front faux pockets. The daughter of Motown superstar Diana Ross wore her hair in a very long single braid. Tracee Ellis Ross is a boss in tailored suit at People's Choice Awards

Descendants star Sofia Carson poses up a storm in ruffled black gown at 2020 People's Choice Awards Her dress had one ruffled shoulder and a ruffled skirt that fell straight from the waist to the floor. A short split at the back of the outfit revealed her black stiletto sandals. Sofia Carson poses in ruffled black gown at People's Choice Awards

Justin Bieber will 'perform several of his hit songs' at the 2020 E! People's Choice Awards The Holy hitmaker is the most-nominated male artist at the upcoming ceremony on November 15 in Santa Monica, California. E! says the pop megastar will 'belt out multiple hit songs.' Justin Bieber will 'perform' at the 2020 E! People's Choice Awards

Chris Pratt is called 'insensitive' and 'tone deaf' for promoting his new Pixar movie with a joke about voting While promoting his new Pixar movie Onward, the 41-year-old actor wrote a caption talking about the importance of voting and encouraging fans to vote for his movie for this year's People's Choice Awards . Chris Pratt is called 'insensitive' for joke about voting

The People's Choice Awards announce their 2020 event WILL happen in November The E! network-hosted event has said they will monitor the pandemic closely and make changes if need be. The People's Choice announce November 2020 date

Sarah Hyland flaunts her toned abs as well as her giant engagement ring from fiance Wells Adams on the way to yoga class She was recently seen rocking her incredible figure in a gorgeous peach gown at the People's Choice Awards, and the TV show that made her a star is soon set to come to an end. Sarah Hyland flaunts her ever toned abs on the way to yoga

Kevin Hart's friends are seen for the first time during recovery after that scary car crash two months ago: 'God was definitely watching over us' Jared Black, 28, who drove the car, and his fiancee Rebecca Broxterman, 31, who is the personal trainer of Hart's wife Eniko Parrish, 35, could be seen in a bad state. Kevin Hart's friends seen for first time during recovery post crash

Maya Jama catches the eye of Kendall Jenner's NBA player ex Ben Simmons as he leaves a VERY flirty comment under her Halloween snap Maya Jama's sexy Halloween snap drove American NBA player Ben Simmons, 23, wild as he couldn't resist leaving two fire emojis in the comments section below. Maya Jama catches the eye of Kendall Jenner's ex Ben Simmons

Pink looks sharp in a long-sleeved gown as she breezes through the red carpet at the CMA Awards with husband Carey Hart and their kids The 40-year-old singer rocked an orange dress and a fedora for the country awards, while her family showed off their own unique style. Pink brings along her husband and kids at the 53rd CMA Awards

Hannah Brown is a wonder in white as she sparks more dating rumors by walking red carpet with DWTS partner Alan Bersten at CMA Awards CMA Awards 2019: Hannah Brown stuns in winter-white gown as she sparks more dating rumors by walking the red carpet with DWTS partner Alan Bersten Hannah Brown walks CMA red carpet with DWTS partner Alan Bersten

Jenna Dewan's daughter Everly kisses her mother's baby bump as the two have a mommy-and-me moment while modeling matching rompers The Step Up actress was seen posing red carpet style with the child, whose father is actor Channing Tatum, as both wore black rompers from fashion line Smash + Tess. Jenna Dewan shows off her baby bump with daughter Everly

Harry Styles shows of his sartorial flair in a quirky sheep print sweater and a striped shirt as he steps out for dinner after Saturday Night Live rehearsals The singer, 25, rocked yet another fabulous ensemble as he donned a quirky Lanvin sheep print sweater, which was navy and covered with fluffy white creatures. Harry Styles shows of his sartorial flair in a sheep print sweater

Kim Kardashian has an impromptu photo shoot at GAS STATION as she strikes a pose with her sisters before the People's Choice Awards Khloe posted several behind-the-scenes snaps from their glamorous night at the awards shows onto her Instagram account, which included the photo of the ladies at the gas station. Kim Kardashian has an impromptu photo shoot at GAS STATION

Gwen Stefani shoots down Blake Shelton engagement rumors after flashing HUGE diamond ring at the People's Choice Awards Gwen Stefani may have rocked a huge diamond ring on the red carpet of the People's Choice Awards on Sunday night, but that doesn't mean she's engaged to Blake Shelton. Gwen Stefani shoots down rumors of her engagement to Blake Shelton

Sarah Hyland is taking her sweet time to set an official wedding date with fiancé Wells Adams: 'We're trying to really just enjoy being engaged!' Sarah Hyland has yet to set a date for her wedding. The 28-year-old actress got engaged to Wells Adams while on vacation in Fiji in July but they are in no rush to tie the knot as they are just enjoying Sarah Hyland is taking her time to set wedding date with Wells Adams

Khloe Kardashian apologizes to fans for not acknowledging best reality star win... as ex Tristan Thompson congratulates her The 35-year-old mother-of-one claimed she had no idea she'd beaten her half-sister Kylie Jenner as well as six others for the trophy Khloe Kardashian apologizes to fans for not realizing reality star win

Jennifer Aniston gets a kiss from Gwen Stefani at the People's Choice Awards after meeting through Brad Pitt and Gavin Rossdale over 15 years ago Jennifer Aniston has been friends with Gwen Stefani for over 10 years after meeting through mutual friends. And on Sunday evening at the 2019 People's Choice Awards in Los Angeles. Jennifer Aniston gets a kiss from longtime pal Gwen Stefani

Kourtney Kardashian leaves little to the imagination as she exposes her bra in a cleavage baring co-ord at the People's Choice Awards With her cleavage fully exposed beneath the lapels of a sequinned monochrome co-ord, Kourtney inevitably turned heads while making her way inside. Kourtney Kardashian exposes her bra at the People's Choice Awards

Kim, Khloe and Kourtney Kardashian go wild as they join momager Kris Jenner at Corey Gamble's very boozy 39th sports-themed bash... (as he tucks into THREE birthday cakes) They spent the evening celebrating at the People's Choice Awards - and Kim Kardashian and her sister Khloe joined her mother Kris Jenner at Corey Gamble's 39th birthday party on Sunday night. Kim Kardashian and Khloe Kardashian at Corey Gamble's 39th birthday

Bellamy Young takes the plunge in sparkling black wrap gown as she sizzles at People's Choice Awards Bellamy Young was a showstopper on the star-studded red carpet for the People's Choice Awards in Los Angeles on Sunday. Bellamy Young takes the plunge in wrap gown at People's Choice Awards

Kandi Burruss puts on a busty display as she and husband Todd Tucker hit the red carpet of the 45th People's Choice Awards Burruss took to her Instagram story on the way over, reminding fans to tune into the awards show, as well as Real Housewives of Atlanta, which aired on the same night. Kandi Burruss puts on a busty display at 45th People's Choice Awards

Brittany Snow dons dazzling black and silver number to the 2019 People's Choice Awards Brittany, 33, oozed elegance as she sashayed down the red carpet in the stunning black and silver number. Snow's dress featured an array of metallic details, with chain mail and zig-zagging lamé. Brittany Snow dons dazzling dress to the 2019 People's Choice Awards

Colton Underwood and Cassie Randolph kiss on red carpet after revealing they track one another by their phone locations Underwood was nominated for The Competition Contestant of 2019 at Sunday's event, but lost out to The Bachelorette's Hannah Brown. The Bachelor's Colton Underwood, girlfriend at People's Choice Awards
